{"article_id":"nlkTwSROcrtCMdRg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Presidential son-in-law and adviser Jared Kushner has had his security clearance downgraded","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"- a move","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that will prevent him from viewing many of the sensitive documents","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"to which he once had unfettered access .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Kushner is not alone .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"All White House aides","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"working on the highest-level interim clearances","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"- at the Top Secret/SCI-level -","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"were informed in a memo","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"sent Friday","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that their clearances would be downgraded to the Secret level ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"according to three people with knowledge of the situation .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"The SCI acronym stands for sensitive compartmented information , a category of information","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that comes from sensitive intelligence sources","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and must be walled off .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"The memo was not signed by chief of staff John Kelly ,","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"but it comes","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"as the retired Marine general and other top White House aides are grappling with the fallout of a scandal","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"involving former White House staff secretary Rob Porter ,","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"which revealed","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"that dozens of White House aides had yet to receive permanent clearances","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"but nonetheless had access to some of the country ' s deepest secrets .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Playbook newsletter","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"Sign up today","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"to receive the # 1-rated newsletter in politics","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"By signing up","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"The president has the ability","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"to grant Kushner a permanent clearance ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"but Trump said Friday","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"- the same day","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"the memo was sent -","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that he was leaving the decision to his chief of staff .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"\" I will let General Kelly make that decision , \"","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Trump told reporters .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" I have no doubt","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"he ' ll make the right decision . \"","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"The White House did not respond to a request for comment on the memo .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders declined to comment on Kushner ' s clearance status at a briefing Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"\" We actually haven ' t commented on Jared ' s issue","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"indicated ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"but we have commented on his ability","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"to do his job .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Which , he ' s a valued member of the team","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"and he will continue to do the important work","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"that he ' s been doing","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"since he ' s started in the administration . \"","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"Kushner ' s attorney Abbe Lowell said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that Kushner \" has done more","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"than what is expected of him in this process . \"","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Lowell added","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"that the changes would \" not affect Mr. Kushner ' s ability","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"to continue to do the very important work","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"he has been assigned by the president . \"","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Friday ' s decision is the first change to the clearance process","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"instituted in the wake of the Porter debacle","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"that will directly affect Kushner ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"who serves as a senior adviser to Trump","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"and until now has had access to the president ' s daily brief , the most highly classified document","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"that Trump sees .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"\" He can not see the PDB ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"not a chance , \"","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"said Bradley Moss , a lawyer","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"who specializes in national security law and clearances .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"\" He no longer has access to a range of intelligence information","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that ordinarily someone in his position and somebody with his responsibilities would normally be privy to","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"in order to perform their functions . \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Moss said","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Kushner and others will be debriefed by officials in the White House security office , an event","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"scheduled to take place Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"according to a person with knowledge of the situation .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"\" They ' re going to give him a list ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"' Here ' s what you ' ve been debriefed from ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"you ' ve been debriefed from this program and that compartment ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"you no longer have any access to it ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"and any breach of that would be a serious security violation and a possible criminal issue . ' \"","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"Kelly took the rare step last week","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"of issuing a public statement","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that Kushner would be able to continue his work in the White House unfettered .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"\" As I told Jared days ago ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"I have full confidence in his ability","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"to continue performing his duties in his foreign policy portfolio","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"including overseeing our Israeli-Palestinian peace effort","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"and serving as an integral part of our relationship with Mexico , \"","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Kelly said in the statement .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"It was unclear whether Kushner would need access to top secret information","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"to continue performing those duties","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"and whether Kelly was personally prepared to enact a policy","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"that could be perceived as a jab at the president ' s son-in-law .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"The decision","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"to downgrade White House staffers","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"still working on interim clearances ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"however ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"indicates","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that Kelly is prepared to impose the same sort of discipline on the White House clearance process","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"that he has tried to impose on the West Wing staff more broadly .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"\" The American people deserve a White House staff","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"that meets the highest standards","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"and that has been carefully vetted","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"- especially those","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"who work closely with the president","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"or handle sensitive national security information , \"","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Kelly told colleagues in a memo","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"circulated on Feb. 16 .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"\" We should","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"- and in the future , must -","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"do better . \"","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Earlier this month , director of National Intelligence Dan Coats said in a Senate Intelligence Committee hearing","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"that people with temporary security clearances should get only limited access to sensitive classified information .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Coats did not mention any specific individuals .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"\" Sometimes it is necessary to have some type of preliminary clearance","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"in order to fill a slot ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"but ... access has to be limited in terms of the kinds of information","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"they can be in a position","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"to receive or not receive , \"","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"Coats said .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"\" It needs to be reformed . \"","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"Kushner has seen his once-expansive West Wing role steadily curtailed since Kelly ' s arrival last July .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"The new chief immediately required Kushner and his wife , first daughter Ivanka Trump , to report through him rather than directly to the president .","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"The pair have also seen their circle of trusted allies shrink in recent weeks .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Reed Cordish ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"who joined the White House early on as part of Kushner ' s Office of American Innovation ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"left the White House earlier this month .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Communications staffer Josh Raffel ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"who handles requests","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"involving Kushner and Ivanka Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"also plans to leave in the next two months ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"according to two people familiar with his decision .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Raffel did not respond to multiple requests for comment .","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"The news of his departure was first reported by Axios .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":269,"left":156,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":149,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":138,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":0,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":1,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":4,"right":147,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":147,"left":143,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":140,"right":142,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":140,"left":5,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":141,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":141,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":11,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":12,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":150,"right":154,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":151,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":19,"right":152,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":152,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":268,"left